### **4. 21_RealTimeFlowGrid**  
**Description:**  
Displays real-time numeric data in a responsive, scrollable chart ideal for dashboards or metric feeds.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeFlowGrid - Live Data Stream Chart

RealTimeFlowGrid visualizes live values from sensors, simulations, or metrics into a scrolling time-based chart.

## Features
- Smooth scrollable line chart  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Built on Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_RealTimeFlowGrid.git
cd 21_RealTimeFlowGrid
python visualize.py
